3. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the complexity of the bin packing problem and provides an approximation algorithm with improved bounds. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses algorithms of Bansal and Lovett-Meka to construct a solution, which are techniques from the field of machine learning.
